@startuml
title Communication Diagram - UC026 ViewMealPlan

allow_mixing
actor "User" as Actor
boundary "ViewMealPlanUI" as UI
control "ViewMealPlanController" as Controller
entity "ViewMealPlanDB" as Entity

Actor -right-> UI : 1: Interact
